ection>\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/component\n - api/component/ReactiveComponentModule\n - guide/component\n - guide/component/let\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/component\n - api/component/LetDirective#createembeddedview\n - api/component/LetDirective#description\n - api/component/LetDirective#letdirective\n - api/component/LetDirective#methods\n - api/component/LetDirective#ngTemplateGuard_ngrxLet\n - api/component/LetDirective#ngmodule\n - api/component/LetDirective#ngondestroy\n - api/component/LetDirective#ngtemplatecontextguard\n - api/component/LetDirective#properties\n - api/component/LetDirective#selectors\n - api/component/LetDirective#static-methods\n - api/component/LetDirective#static-properties\n - api/component/LetDirective#subscription\n - api/component/PushPipe\n - api/component/ReactiveComponentModule\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/modules/component/src/let/let.directive.ts?message=docs(component)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L142-L148\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/modules/component/src/let/let.directive.ts?message=docs(component)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L170-L177\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/modules/component/src/let/let.directive.ts?message=docs(component)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L178-L181\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/modules/component/src/let/let.directive.ts?message=docs(component)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L25-L182\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/tree/13.0.2/modules/component/src/let/let.directive.ts#L142-L148\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/tree/13.0.2/modules/component/src/let/let.directive.ts#L170-L177\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/tree/13.0.2/modules/component/src/let/let.directive.ts#L178-L181\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/tree/13.0.2/modules/component/src/let/let.directive.ts#L25-L182\n-->"
